routeDesc: This route was implemented when the app was still not working properly and cut off half the walk!
A route that follows the perimeter of the available back fields.
Follows the bridleway and then goes down into woods behind the paintball place

routeHazards.hazardName: Bridleway, there are sometimes horses with riders walking down here

routeDesc: Down into the woods from the car park, then round the fields to get back up

routeHazards.hazardName: Car park next to a busy road - quickly left behind
Near the train tracks - could be loud
Adjacent field sometimes has sheep in

routeDesc: Walk along the bridleway and down through the woods into the fields, round and back up to the car park

routeHazards.hazardName: Car park and a very quiet road, leads into bridleway - sometimes horses around
Entrance to the fields which is gated, there is sometimes livestock in here
Public footpath behind the paintball place, though it's usually only open at the weekend
Public footpath that leads to a field that 9/10 has sheep in

routeDesc: Around the outside of the woods, ignoring the fields

routeHazards.hazardName: Very busy road here, but quickly left behind

routeDesc: Walking around most of the woods, a rather hilly walk through the woods

routeHazards.hazardName: Bike jumps here, careful of cyclists
